===Glyph origin===
{{Han etyl}}
{{liushu|p}}. The original meaning is uncertain.

Proposed interpretations include:
* A weaving tool (e.g., a spool or bobbin), related to {{zh-l|榺|tr=shèng}};
* A carrying pole, making it the original form of {{zh-l|任}};
* A double-bladed axe.

